Adding better api functionality.
- Event#index now returns better information about the events returned, offset, limit, total, and placeholders for next and previous. - User#index now returns better information, just like the Event#index method. - Implemented serializable_has on events, which nests info a little bit, but to prevent stack exploding, not everything. - Tags now serialize better, and has many events. - User now serialize better, has many events, and a self_link url instead of self_link self. - Removed the jbuilder files, they are not needed. - Allow to get users from the api. - CHanged it so that events now container their own positions instead of having separate model for position. Will need to remove the position model and implement the methods to get events based on position later.

- Different message if the authorization token doesn't exist, might add another message if it is missing completely. - Handles some errors in events_controller. - Code now does next and previous links correctly in events controller. - Implemented a method for events created by a user. - Changed to respond_with on the update function. - raise_bad_format and ErrorMessage in events_controller. Might refactor out this. - Added routes for select on user and select on tag methods.
